# Docker Conventions

- Local development uses `docker-compose.yml` at project root.
- Each app has its own `Dockerfile` in `apps/{name}/Dockerfile`.
- Use multi-stage builds: `deps` ‚Üí `build` ‚Üí `runtime` stages.
- Base image: `node:20-alpine`.
- Postgres version: 16-alpine.
- Environment variables are defined in `docker-compose.yml` for dev; use `.env` files for overrides (never commit `.env`).
